3
00:01:51,972 --> 00:01:53,039
-Take care of her.

4
00:01:53,072 --> 00:01:54,872
You gave your word.

5
00:02:02,805 --> 00:02:03,272
-Huh?

6
00:02:13,451 --> 00:02:15,505
[whimpers] Mr. Stalker?

7
00:02:15,539 --> 00:02:16,339
Hello, Mister?

8
00:02:16,372 --> 00:02:18,639
Where are you right now?

9
00:02:18,672 --> 00:02:22,072
Do-- do you think we
could stop this game?

10
00:02:22,105 --> 00:02:22,905
-Huh?

11
00:02:22,939 --> 00:02:23,605
MAN: Stalker?

12
00:02:23,639 --> 00:02:24,872
Where'd she get that?

13
00:02:24,905 --> 00:02:27,939
What's with the new
attitude all of a sudden?

14
00:02:34,105 --> 00:02:35,605
LIGHT (VOICEOVER):
Just as I thought.

15
00:02:35,639 --> 00:02:37,772
As long as I still
have Ryuk's notebook,

16
00:02:37,805 --> 00:02:41,305
even though I gave up Rem's, all
awareness I have of Rem still

17
00:02:41,339 --> 00:02:42,639
remains.

18
00:02:42,672 --> 00:02:46,005
Rem, the only reason I have
to go through all this trouble

19
00:02:46,039 --> 00:02:50,205
is because you brought another
Death Note to the human world.

20
00:02:50,239 --> 00:02:53,439
-Is this really what
you want, Light?

21
00:02:53,472 --> 00:02:56,239
-Yeah.

22
00:02:56,272 --> 00:02:57,239
-OK.

23
00:02:57,272 --> 00:02:59,039
I never thought the
Death Note I gave

24
00:02:59,072 --> 00:03:01,772
you would end up
buried and abandoned.

25
00:03:01,805 --> 00:03:03,272
Listen, Ryuk.

26
00:03:03,305 --> 00:03:05,572
For the time being,
I'm just hiding it.

27
00:03:05,605 --> 00:03:09,272
But it stays mine,
until the next time

28
00:03:09,305 --> 00:03:13,239
you hear me say the following
words-- get rid of it.

29
00:03:13,272 --> 00:03:15,839
When I say that,
regardless of the context,

30
00:03:15,872 --> 00:03:19,139
assume that I want to relinquish
ownership of this Death Note.

31
00:03:19,172 --> 00:03:21,005
-Got it.

32
00:03:21,039 --> 00:03:21,905
-Mr. Stalker?

33
00:03:21,939 --> 00:03:22,872
This is illegal.

34
00:03:22,905 --> 00:03:24,272
You have to stop.

35
00:03:24,305 --> 00:03:24,839
OK?

36
00:03:24,872 --> 00:03:26,339
Come on, please?

37
00:03:26,372 --> 00:03:28,439
-She's been acting
like this ever

38
00:03:28,472 --> 00:03:30,605
since she regained
consciousness.

39
00:03:30,639 --> 00:03:32,005
-Seriously.

40
00:03:32,039 --> 00:03:34,439
Does she think she can get out
of this just by playing dumb?

41
00:03:34,472 --> 00:03:35,072
-OK.

42
00:03:35,105 --> 00:03:36,405
How about this?

43
00:03:36,439 --> 00:03:38,105
You could at least
take off my blindfold.

44
00:03:38,139 --> 00:03:39,205
Don't you think?

45
00:03:39,239 --> 00:03:43,339
It'll be nice to see
what you look like.

46
00:03:43,372 --> 00:03:45,472
-Matsuda, call Mogi for me.

47
00:03:45,505 --> 00:03:46,639
-Huh?

48
00:03:46,672 --> 00:03:49,739
Just a second.

49
00:03:49,772 --> 00:03:51,139
Here.

50
00:03:51,172 --> 00:03:53,939
-Mr. Mogi, when you apprehended
Misa Amane, you made it clear

51
00:03:53,972 --> 00:03:56,172
that she was a
suspect, am I correct?

52
00:03:56,205 --> 00:03:58,472
-Yes, like you told me.

53
00:03:58,505 --> 00:04:00,739
First, I blindfolded her
and covered her mouth.

54
00:04:00,772 --> 00:04:03,805
I told her that we knew
she was the second Kira.

55
00:04:03,839 --> 00:04:05,705
I made sure that she heard me.

56
00:04:05,739 --> 00:04:08,205
She didn't struggle when I put
the blindfold and handcuffs

57
00:04:08,239 --> 00:04:09,039
on her.

58
00:04:09,072 --> 00:04:10,805
