59
00:04:10,839 --> 00:04:14,005
-What if I gave you an
autograph, or shook your hang?

60
00:04:14,039 --> 00:04:15,139
I know.

61
00:04:15,172 --> 00:04:16,772
I can give you a kiss on
the cheek of you want.

62
00:04:16,805 --> 00:04:17,672
Oh, come on.

63
00:04:17,705 --> 00:04:18,605
I won't run away.

64
00:04:18,639 --> 00:04:19,972
I promise.

65
00:04:20,005 --> 00:04:22,572
L (VOICEOVER): We'd already
made so much progress with her,

66
00:04:22,605 --> 00:04:23,872
