talking about a stalker?

68
00:04:28,339 --> 00:04:30,005
DISTORTED VOICE (ON
SPEAKER): Misa Amane.

69
00:04:30,039 --> 00:04:30,772
-Huh?

70
00:04:30,805 --> 00:04:32,339
What's that, Mr. Stalker?

71
00:04:32,372 --> 00:04:33,839
Are you planning to release me?

72
00:04:33,872 --> 00:04:36,005
DISTORTED VOICE (ON SPEAKER):
Before you passed out,

73
00:04:36,039 --> 00:04:37,205
you barely spoke.

74
00:04:37,239 --> 00:04:39,472
And you even asked
me to kill you.

75
00:04:39,505 --> 00:04:40,905
And now you're
claiming ignorance?

76
00:04:40,939 --> 00:04:41,572
-Hm?

77
00:04:41,605 --> 00:04:42,905
I don't understand.

78
00:04:42,939 --> 00:04:45,272
I mean, you're the one who
knocked me out and then brought

79
00:04:45,305 --> 00:04:46,372
me here, remember?

80
00:04:46,405 --> 00:04:47,072
Wait.

81
00:04:47,105 --> 00:04:48,439
I get it.

82
00:04:48,472 --> 00:04:52,239
