interrogation fantasy, right?

83
00:04:52,272 --> 00:04:53,605
-Huh?

84
00:04:53,639 --> 00:04:55,305
-Do you know why I'm
detaining you here?

85
00:04:55,339 --> 00:04:56,305
You must have some idea.

86
00:04:56,339 --> 00:04:57,805
MISA (ON SPEAKER):
What do you mean?

87
00:04:57,839 --> 00:04:59,505
Because I'm a
celebrity, obviously.

88
00:04:59,539 --> 00:05:01,572
But you're definitely
the first stalker

89
00:05:01,605 --> 00:05:02,705
