this, so cut it out.

93
00:05:09,205 --> 00:05:10,939
-Oh, this is scary.

94
00:05:10,972 --> 00:05:12,072
What's going on?

95
00:05:12,105 --> 00:05:13,572
I can't stand it anymore!

96
00:05:13,605 --> 00:05:15,072
Please let me go!

97
00:05:15,105 --> 00:05:17,072
You have to let me go!

98
00:05:17,105 --> 00:05:19,072
I-- I need to go
to the bathroom.

99
00:05:19,105 --> 00:05:20,905
I have to go to the
bathroom again, OK?

100
00:05:20,939 --> 00:05:22,205
DISTORTED VOICE (ON
SPEAKER): It's only

101
